OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Poetic' and 'notorious'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsculptor Serra dies        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Richard Serra, a giant of US art whose 
OL,6, monumental steel sculptures have       
OL,7, appeared around the world over the past
OL,8, 50 years, has died at the age of 85.   
OL,10,FNicknamed the "poet of iron", Serra is 
OL,11,Fcredited with reinventing sculpture by 
OL,12,Fplacing simple but huge arrangements of
OL,13,Fupright slabs and shapes in the ground.
OL,15,FPeople can walk around and between his 
OL,16,Flooming and leaning metal sheets, often
OL,17,Fon a street or in the landscape.       
OL,19,FHis rusting works are in cities        
OL,20,Fincluding London, Berlin and New York. 
